<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Schwäbisch Hall</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Fürsprache zugunsten des Jakob Topler, Bürger zu Nürnberg, bei einem dort von Friedrich III. Schenk von Limpurg mit Götz von Berlichingen angesetzten Gerichtstag.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_28" id="13v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_28_r4l1">Der Stat cʒu halle </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_28_r4l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> vns hat fürgelegt Jacob Topler <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> / vvie daʒ der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l3">Edell / her <expan>fr<ex>iedrich</ex></expan> Schenck <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> cʒu <expan>Lẏmp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / cʒwiſchen Jm / vnd Göcʒen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l4">von Berlichingen vnd auch hanſen von Aẏchelheim / einen tag cʒu ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l5">gen halle beredt vnd gemacht hab / der do ſein ſülle 
<del rend="strikethrough"> auf </del> nu biſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l6">freẏtag v̈ber acht tag / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> ~ etlıche </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l7">ewrs Rats durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>leih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / die Jm auff <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l11">tag 
<add><ab facs="#facs_28_line_1576489769781_6850">in ſeinen ſachen </ab></add> geraten <expan>fürderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd beẏgeſtendig ſein / Als etc / das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_28_r4l12"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıııj̃ poſt <expan>Michael<ex>is</ex></expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_28" id="13v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Halle </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Jacob Topler,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz der edell her
                                <expan>Fr<ex>iedrich</ex></expan> Schenck,
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> czu <expan>lymp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>,
                        czwischen im und Göczen von Berlichingen und auch Hansen von Aychelheim
                        einen tag czu ew gen Halle beredt und gemacht hab, der do sein sülle nu bisz
                        <app><note><q type="date">freytag über acht tag</q>11.10.1409</note></app>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir dem
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> etliche ewrs rats durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>leih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet, die im auff
                            <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag <add>in seinen sachen</add>
                        geraten, <expan>fürderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und beygestendig sein, als
                        etc. Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iiii post
                        <expan>Michael<ex>is</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
